{"tid":1301021,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"NOW政情：林鄭講話效果不大　建制派人人自危","createTime":"2019-07-09T13:57:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T17:03:42.000Z","uid":2617,"like":797,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":133,"replies":[{"pid":"3f5ead93c47bc667ccc3e7ed098ab3b323e91725","tid":1301021,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T13:57:53.000Z","msg":"【政情】網民熱烈贈慶 民建聯連環取消黨慶活動<br />\n11分鐘前<br />\n【Now新聞台】神隱一星期，行政長官林鄭月娥終於露面。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭主持暑假前最後一次行政會議，會前見記者超過半小時，透露最近與多人會面，提出五大施政新風聽民意。對於示威者的五大訴求，立場無變，用字有變，修例最新用上「壽終正寢」，「撤回」二字始終未有宣之於口。<br />\n<br />\n多名左派人士向《政情》透露，中聯辦事前事後都向他們打聽，對林鄭最新回應的意見及評估。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不少左派人士都認為，她的態度及用語已有改善，但政府立場始終不變，無助改變目前對立的局面，評估林鄭的講話效果不大。<br />\n<br />\n加上左派研判，反修例行動已遍地開花，遊行地點蔓延至九龍新界，針對的亦不只是特區政府，而是整個建制派陣營，人人自危亦要人人自保。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n首當其衝的是民建聯，踏入民建聯的生日月，多個黨慶活動要取消，包括兩年一度的大型黨慶酒會，原定周二於港交所舉行，特區政府及中聯辦領導早答應出席，但最終在酒會前夕決定取消。黨內顧慮到賓客的安全及交通問題，加上網上開始號召包圍酒會，唯有向嘉賓逐個解釋取消酒會。<br />\n<br />\n地區黨慶活動亦不能倖免，民建聯九龍西支部月中，將於旺角一間酒樓舉辦會慶聚餐，據了解，領導層傾向取消，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">除了早前有網民發起買位賀壽，最近亦有人計劃，以民建聯賀壽為主題申請遊行，正考慮取消以免引起衝突。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n行會暑假休會近兩個月，林鄭月娥大可閉關避風頭，但建制政黨面對區選在即，難以整個暑假都「潛水」避戰。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=354835&amp;home=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D354835%26home%3D1&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBLHKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=d1163f3f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D354835%26home%3D1&h=f170f458\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=354835&amp;home=1</a>"},{"pid":"d1c5f5c1f9bedf0c702f1dad473709275ec7abea","tid":1301021,"uid":886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T13:58:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eb3789a7d90d9d8b798b94871fa733119bd8f55","tid":1301021,"uid":2617,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"d1c5f5c1f9bedf0c702f1dad473709275ec7abea","tid":1301021,"uid":886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T13:58:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T13:58:40.000Z","msg":"ＣＬＳ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d22f8bd00ec37b7ed0f111d8714349bfc6874fb","tid":1301021,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T14:00:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"930eccc9ddb5a26aaa4bcd117f311ec887577dea","tid":1301021,"uid":2617,"like":129,"dislike":0,"score":129,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T14:00:44.000Z","msg":"林鄭的講話效果不大。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b868dc0dc30fd9e141389143f0c9aa61c3a3cff","tid":1301021,"uid":60527,"like":177,"dislike":0,"score":177,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T14:02:44.000Z","msg":"賀壽遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b84e2ece992668b8f92129c7ec6e393ce25a5a0e","tid":1301021,"uid":61105,"like":242,"dislike":0,"score":242,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T14:02:48.000Z","msg":"香討班ching真係勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88aee1a5f9ea140cada6ac9b7cb493b2af5be4ac","tid":1301021,"uid":2617,"like":74,"dislike":0,"score":74,"quote":{"pid":"b84e2ece992668b8f92129c7ec6e393ce25a5a0e","tid":1301021,"uid":61105,"like":242,"dislike":0,"score":242,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T14:02:48.000Z","msg":"香討班ching真係勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T14:03:34.000Z","msg